; Coverage test for filters.cc lines 1296
; Tests transfer_details with SET_PAYEE.
; Line 1296: SET_PAYEE path renames payee based on expression
; --payee=account renames the payee to the account name.

2024/01/15 Groceries
    Expenses:Food             $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --payee=account
24-Jan-15 Expenses:Food         Expenses:Food                $50.00       $50.00
24-Jan-15 Assets:Cash           Assets:Cash                 $-50.00            0
end test
